# ── Contact form delivery (server-side — set in Vercel for all environments,
#    and locally in .env.local). NO NEXT_PUBLIC prefix: these keys are used
#    only inside app/api/enquiry/route.ts and never reach the browser.

# Attio — the system of record for enquiries. Every submission upserts the
# person, attaches the enquiry as a note, and creates a follow-up task with a
# 24h deadline.
#   Attio → Workspace settings → Developers → API keys.
#   Scopes: Record read-write · Note read-write · Task read-write ·
#           Object configuration read.
ATTIO_API_KEY=

# Resend — sends the bilingual auto-reply to the enquirer and the internal
# notification to hello@katamedia.cc.
#   resend.com → API Keys. The domain katamedia.cc must be VERIFIED
#   (Resend → Domains → add katamedia.cc → set the DNS records it shows)
#   before "from: hello@katamedia.cc" is allowed.
RESEND_API_KEY=

# ── Legacy (retired) ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# NEXT_PUBLIC_WEB3FORMS_KEY was the old Web3Forms delivery. No longer read by
# any code — remove it from Vercel once the new route is live.
